description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Gaston purrs with a rating of 59, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 295, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Box for East, Stringalong for South, and Nine Lives for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60595-14790-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [295 Votes, Top 5% Score]
